n s\u1ed1 50 t\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng.&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-u23-chau-a-tag11263.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018</span></span>, t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 l\u1edbn lao v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u1ec1 v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn con s\u1ed1 50 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam co duoc cai tet am no nho thanh cong tai VCK U23 chau A.\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i t\u1ebft \u1ea5m no nh\u1edd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/tien-thuong-u23-viet-nam-va-tiet-lo-day-buc-xuc-tu-tro-ly-doi-tuyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ee9c x\u00fac cho \u0111\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 quan t\u00e2m l\u00e0 li\u1ec7u kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn tay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd. Theo <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-viet-thu-cam-dong-sau-chien-tich-cua-u23-168-178629.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef L\u00ea Huy Khoa</span></span>, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 t\u00e2m, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 \u0103n theo hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Bongda24h.vn xin tr\u00edch l\u1ea1i chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd L\u00ea Huy Khoa \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u1eb3ng hi\u1ec3u th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y (s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 50 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng - PV) \u0111\u00e2u ra v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c hay kh\u00f4ng n\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n v\u1eadt th\u00ec u 23 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 3 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y m\u1eb7t m\u0169i \u0111\u00e2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 lo\u1ea1i tr\u1eddi \u01a1i: cho \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111\u00eam v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi , d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn sai ng\u01b0\u1eddi, kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e2n r\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n t\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u00e2n ... \u0103n theo, n\u00f3i xong ch\u1edd c\u1ee9t tr\u00e2u h\u00f3a b\u00f9n c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 n\u00ean c\u00f4ng khai nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a h\u00e3o kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ec9?</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hay \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00ecnh thay m\u1eb7t U23 \u0111i h\u1ecfi, ch\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u1ecd th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 m\u1eb7t m\u0169i \u0111i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh em U23 \u0111ang b\u1ee9c x\u00fac&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/so-tien-thuong-cho-dt-u23-viet-nam-da-vuot-moc-50-ty-dong-168-183221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/12/so-tien-thuong-cho-dt-u23-viet-nam-da-vuot-moc-50-ty-dong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/so-tien-thuong-cho-dt-u23-viet-nam-da-vuot-moc-50-ty-dong-168-183221.html\">S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea1t c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c kh\u1ee7ng</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb VFF, ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00c1 qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c 50 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"814","checkdouble":"183561"},{"date":"10:29 05/04","title":"\"Barca ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng