nh ho\u00e0ng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-4 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Italia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV n\u00e0y v\u1eabn t\u00ecm ra l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i, khi cho r\u1eb1ng Barca th\u1eafng nh\u1edd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pique v\u00e0 Suarez, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 2 pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Roma khi\u1ebfn c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t. Nh\u01b0ng Di Francesco v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi r\u1eddi v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 h\u1ecd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;D\u00f9 sao, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Barca d\u1ec5 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca, De Rossi \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m sai l\u1ea7m, Manolas c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng may v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap Barca h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Roma\" title=\"Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap Barca h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Roma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/barca-chi-thang-vi-duoc-trong-tai-giup-suc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap Barca h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Roma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh cho d\u00f9 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi Semedo ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Dzeko, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Pellegrini.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng&rdquo; &ndash; Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Roma ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7, tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng, t\u1ea1i sao l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ec9? K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111ang nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 Barca, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Barca ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1edd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 may m\u1eafn, HLV Ernesto Valverde \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3: &ldquo;M\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ri\u00eang h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, d\u00f9 3-0 th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n 4-1. D\u00f9 sao, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i Barca c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca vs Roma</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088597/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Barcelona 4-1 Roma<br>\r\n</span><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-tro-barca-len-mat-thang-nho-phan-luoi-thi-sao-chu-184-183552.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/thay-tro-barca-len-mat-thang-nho-phan-luoi-thi-sao-chu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/thay-tro-barca-len-mat-thang-nho-phan-luoi-thi-sao-chu-184-183552.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Barca l\u00ean m\u1eb7t: Th\u1eafng nh\u1edd ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi, th\u00ec sao ch\u1ee9?</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ebfp l\u1eddi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Ernesto Valverde, c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Gerard Pique hay Luis Suarez \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Barca 4-1 Roma l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"813","checkdouble":"183564"},{"date":"10:49 05/04","title":"Ibra n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a CR7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/ibra-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-sieu-pham-cua-cr7.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{p