9m, v\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 Zlatan Ibrahimovic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ngo\u1ea1i l\u1ec7.</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng oanh li\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus v\u1eeba qua, Cristiano Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Buffon, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Real Madrid g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea3 2 ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf Zlatan Ibrahimovic \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i CR7. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;\u1ed2, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9. So s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf MLS \u01b0? T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn trong pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf Champions League, c\u00f2n t\u00f4i ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf MLS, <strong>\u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn</strong>&rdquo; &ndash; Ibra th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean ESPN.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/barzagli-tam-phuc-khau-phuc-ban-thang-cua-ronaldo-se-di-vao-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" title=\"bong da 24h\" type=\"bong da 24h\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span></span> c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1. Nh\u01b0ng khi b\u1ea1n ghi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Ibra c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. <strong>Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean th\u1eed ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n t\u1eeb kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 40m v\u00e0 xem n\u00f3 c\u00f3 v\u00e0o hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ibra n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i MLS</h2>\r\n<div><br>\r\nSau khi chia s\u1ebb c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 36 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9, n\u01a1i anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft LA Galaxy: &ldquo;Khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ki\u1ec3u nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u 40 tr\u1eadn trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 v\u1eady khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, t\u00f4i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u00e2ng l\u00ean r\u1ea5t cao. T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic trong mau ao LA Galaxy\" title=\"Ibrahimovic trong mau ao LA Galaxy\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/ibra-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-sieu-pham-cua-cr7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ibrahimovic trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o LA Galaxy</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf M\u1ef9 kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a LA Galaxy v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, HLV, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Ibra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Zlatan, c\u00e1c C\u0110V v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi MLS \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m, Ibra s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1ef9, n\u01a1i anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-khien-ca-the-gioi-can-loi-khi-lap-sieu-pham-vao-luoi-juve-184-183489.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/ronaldo-khien-ca-the-gioi-can-loi-khi-lap-sieu-pham-vao-luoi-juve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-khien-ca-the-gioi-can-loi-khi-lap-sieu-pham-vao-luoi-juve-184-183489.html\">Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi &ldquo;c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi&rdquo; khi l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Juve</span><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Italia ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cris Ronaldo l\u1eadp si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Gianluigi Buffon.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"812","checkdouble":"183565"},{"date":"11:16 05/04","title":"Fan Liverpool b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i v\u00ec t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xe bus c\u1ee7a Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/fan-liverpool-bi-chi-trich-du-doi-vi-tan-cong-xe-bus-cua-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe 