 ch\u1edf g\u00e1i l\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a anh cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, The Sun cho bi\u1ebft.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien dao Rooney bao tron ky nghi mung sinh nhat cua vo hinh anh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rooney bao tr\u1ecdn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Tien-dao-Rooney-bao-tron-ky-nghi-mung-sinh-nhat-cua-vo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec u\u1ed1ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u l\u00e1i xe v\u00e0 ch\u1edf g\u00e1i l\u1ea1 7 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Rooney n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00f2ng tin c\u1ee7a Coleen, h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ed3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c. \u1ea2nh: Instagram.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb9 con Coleen s\u1ebd \u1edf resort Madinat Jumeirah c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 kho\u1ea3ng 1.500 b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed7i \u0111\u00eam. Khu ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00f3 b\u00e3i bi\u1ec3n ri\u00eang, c\u00f3 spa \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng 50 nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5. Trong khi v\u1ee3 con vui ch\u01a1i \u1edf Dubai, Rooney v\u1eabn \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anh v\u00ec b\u1eadn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Everton. Ch\u00e0ng Shrek qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u1edf nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd \"ngoan\", nghi\u00eam ch\u1ec9nh ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00eam b\u00f9 kh\u00fa r\u1ed3i g\u1eb7p n\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 7 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c su\u00fdt tan v\u1ee1 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i sau v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c u\u1ed1ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u l\u00e1i xe, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng Wayne quy\u1ebft tr\u00e1nh xa r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i khi v\u1ee3 v\u1eafng nh\u00e0. Coleen \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tha th\u1ee9 cho ch\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 Wayne th\u1ec1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ed3ng, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eabu sau s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 y\u00eau chi\u1ec1u Coleen, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1eb1ng anh y\u00eau c\u00f4 t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. C\u00f4 \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Dubai nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng Wayne mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3. Anh \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 v\u00ec v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ra s\u00e2n. L\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Wayne c\u01b0 x\u1eed t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 khi Coleen v\u00e0 l\u0169 tr\u1ebb \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh xa r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i\", ngu\u1ed3n tin cho bi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eeba \u0111\u00f3n con trai th\u1ee9 t\u01b0, b\u00e9 Cass Mac h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng hai. V\u00e0i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Rooney b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec u\u1ed1ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u l\u00e1i xe, treo b\u1eb1ng l\u00e1i hai n\u0103m v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i lao \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f4ng \u00edch. Coleen c\u00f9ng ba con trai \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf Majorca th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, ph\u1ea3i t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 v\u00ec ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1edf c\u00f4 n\u00e0ng ti\u1ec7c t\u00f9ng Laura Simpson tr\u00ean xe. Trong b\u1ee9c t\u00e2m th\u01b0 chia s\u1ebb r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd tha th\u1ee9 cho ch\u00e0ng Shrek, Coleen th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chia tay nh\u01b0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho ch\u1ed3ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00ec c\u00f4 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n y\u00eau anh, mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef gia \u0111\u00ecnh cho c\u00e1c con.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ngoisao.net<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"808","checkdouble":"183518"},{"date":"15:21 04/04","title":"WAGs tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn Nga d\u00f9 nguy hi\u1ec3m","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/wags-tuyen-thu-anh-quyet-den-nga-du-nguy-hiem.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerela