=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah toa sang va chan thuong trong tran Liverpool 3-0 Man City hinh anh\" title=\"Salah t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Liverpool-3-0-Man-City-Con-benh-giao-dieu-cua-Pep-Guardiola-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5p th\u1ecfm \u00e2u lo khi s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1eb7ng nh\u1eb9. Tuy nhi\u00ean ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1ea1i xoay quanh th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Kh\u00f4ng sao h\u1ebft, ch\u00ednh c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n th\u1ecfa n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i s\u00e1t sao th\u00eam v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng Kopites n\u00e0o mong mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u1ea3nh thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn derby Merseyside v\u1edbi Everton c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u00fap C1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Man City, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Salah hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi 38 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, trong \u0111\u00f3 29 gi\u00fap anh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch an to\u00e0n v\u1edbi Harry Kane, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088663/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Liverpool 3-0 Man City</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"798","checkdouble":"183543"},{"date":"06:02 05/04","title":"Liverpool 3-0 Man City: C\u01a1n b\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/du-am-liverpool-30-man-city.j