</o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ecb th\u1ebf chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia t\u00e2n ti\u1ebfn, l\u1ed7i l\u1ea1c v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb suy chuy\u1ec3n b\u1edfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00edch s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn knock-out Champions League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">23 l\u1ea7n xa nh\u00e0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 c\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u giai \u0111o\u1ea1n hai, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Pep ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 5 th\u1eafng, trong khi h\u00f2a 10 v\u00e0 thua t\u1eadn 9. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ph\u1ea7n \u0111a c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eb5n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf Camp Nou, Allianz hay Etihad hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pep Guardiola Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" title=\"Pep Guardiola Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Untitled.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola trong th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i Liverpool 3-0 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1eady th\u00ec t\u1ea1i sao m\u1ed9t HLV k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u1edf c\u00e1c chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n c\u00fap C1 c\u1ee7a Barcelona, Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Man City, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng \u1edf ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng? Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng Pep \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang qu\u00e1 m\u00e1y m\u00f3c, gi\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd &ldquo;t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 l\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 \u1ee9ng bi\u1ebfn linh ho\u1ea1t sao cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111a d\u1ea1ng t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong \u0111\u00eam kinh ho\u00e0ng b\u1ecb Liverpool v\u00f9i d\u1eadp th\u1ea3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Pep \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn Man City tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ng\u00e2y th\u01a1 v\u00e0 h\u1edb h\u00eanh. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1ecf t\u01b0\u1eddng trong hai b\u00e0n thua ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e2ng qu\u00e1 cao r\u1ed3i b\u1ecf qu\u00ean ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n khu v\u1ef1c trung l\u1ed9, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho pha b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Mo Salah hay c\u00fa s\u00fat xa s\u1ea5m s\u00e9t c\u1ee7a Alex Chamberlain.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thua, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ng\u1eebng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.&rdquo;</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Pep th\u1eadt hay, th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 nhi\u1ec7t li\u1ec7t. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 t\u00f9y c\u01a1 \u1ee9ng bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 tr\u00e1nh b\u1ea3o th\u1ee7 c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc, b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Man City \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Anfield v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-thieu-rui-man-city-trong-con-dien-anfield-184-183529.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/liverpool-thieu-rui-man-city-trong-con-dien-anfield.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-thieu-rui-man-city-trong-con-dien-anfield-184-183529.html\">Liverpool: Thi\u00eau r\u1ee5i Man City trong c\u01a1n \u0111i\u00ean Anfield</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;B\u1ecdn h\u1ecd co c\u1ee5m v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c ch\u1ecbu h\u00e0nh h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bu\u00f4ng tha ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o m\u1ecdi d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 s\u1ed1ng ch\u01b0a b\u1ecb h\u00fat c\u1ea1n.&rdquo; &ndash; Kopites ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Salah \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n, v\u00ec&hellip; \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ed quy\u1ebft n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eb1ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u0103ng hoa t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec9nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Mo Salah v\u1edbi 38 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 6-10 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf Anfield? B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1ef1a l\u1ebd hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00e0m n\u1ed5 tung c\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">May m\u1eafn &ldquo;ph\u00e1&rdquo; b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Man City, Salah b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khu c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi x\u1ebb b\u00f3ng sang ph\u1ea3i theo \u0111\u00e0 tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Roberto Firmino. N\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Ederson \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 l\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec5nh ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Kyle Walker, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Firmino gh\u00e9 ch\u00e2n ch\u00edch b\u00f3ng sang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ee9ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n cho Salah tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City Con benh giao dieu cua Pep Guardiola hinh anh 2\" title=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City C\u01a1n b\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Liverpool-3-0-Man-City-Con-benh-giao-dieu-cua-Pep-Guardiola-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Salah ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng trung phong c\u1eafm truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u01a1n \u1edf c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay c\u1ee7a Firmino. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eadt th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u0129nh c\u1eedu c\u1ee7a Salah v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n theo c\u00e1ch tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb h\u01a1i&hellip; t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eb3ng sao h\u1ebft, ch\u1eebng n\u00e0o Salah ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm ra gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng ai r\u1ea3nh h\u01a1i ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n n\u00e0y n\u1ecd v\u1ec1 anh. Messi Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n, v\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n v\u00ec&hellip; \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ed5 \u1ea5m&rdquo; \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o tr\u00e1ch c\u1ee9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi Sterling ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong m\u1ed7i chuy\u1ebfn tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 x\u01b0a Anfield v\u00e0 b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng hu\u00fdt s\u00e1o, la \u00f3, ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a&hellip;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sterling\" title=\"Sterling\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/skynews-raheem-sterling-man-city_4186035-696x391.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i trong th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Anfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi g\u1ea7n c\u1ea3 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 tr\u00f4i qua m\u00e0 Man City v\u1eabn b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 v\u1edbt v\u00e1t danh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng, Pep kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m tin cho Sterling, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i h\u01a1n n\u1eeda gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng n\u00e3o n\u1ec1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 ba th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ea1ch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh b\u1ecb c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh hi\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ecba Anfield, Sterling d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ngoan ngo\u00e3n n\u1eb1m trong t\u00fai qu\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Andy Robertson. M\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 v\u00f4 v\u1ecb, v\u1edbi \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ebfm hoi c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng sau pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Georginio Wijnaldum hay c\u1ea3 pha va ch\u1ea1m h\u1eb1m h\u00e8 v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 ki\u00eam \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Jordan Henderson.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n thua -&nbsp; Li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a, Liverpool?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quy\u1ec7n l\u1eabn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch v\u00e0 th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong v\u00f2ng ba th\u00e1ng, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u c\u0169ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i lu\u1ea9n qu\u1ea9n v\u1edbi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ho\u00e0i nghi d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp: Li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">3-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi n\u00e0y, Man City s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u00edt \u1ecfi \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e9m \u0111i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ba b\u00e0n t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng v\u00f4 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng san l\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Liverpool c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thua PSG \u0111\u00e2u, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9ng nh\u00e2n t\u1eeb Watford \u0111\u1ebfn Sevilla trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City Con benh giao dieu cua Pep Guardiola hinh anh 4\" title=\"Liverpool 3-0 Man City C\u01a1n b\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/liverpool-30-man-city-con-benh-giao-dieu-cua-pep-guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u00f9i d\u1eadp Man City, Liverpool \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 nh\u01b0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy v\u1eady th\u00ec m\u1ed1i \u00e2u lo cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man City v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng fan trung l\u1eadp, r\u1eb1ng Liverpool d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield c\u1ee7a qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n Virgil Van Dijk \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh hay vi\u1ec7c Loris Karius th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Simon Mignolet b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong khung th\u00e0nh, nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m s\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb3ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Liverpool d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ba b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 30 ph\u00fat b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 ng\u1ee3i khen h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho The Kop sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">90 ph\u00fat th\u1eed th\u00e1ch s\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 b\u00e3o t\u00e1p \u1edf Etihad n\u1eefa th\u00f4i, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch ph\u00e2n ly Liverpool v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 m\u00f2n m\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/14088663/013100\" rel=\"nofollow\">Liverpool 3-0 Man City</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-liverpool-vs-man-city-01h45-ngay-54-champions-league-201718-372-183531.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/4/ket-qua-liverpool-vs-man-city-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-liverpool-vs-man-city-01h45-ngay-54-champions-league-201718-372-183531.html\">Liverpool 3-0 Man City: H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t vua n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, The Klopp ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd m\u1ed9t Man City ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng quang t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda l\u1ea1i thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 tin \u1edf tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"797","checkdouble":"183544"},{"date":"07:04 05/04","title":"Guardiola: \u201cThua Liverpool 0-3 n\u00e0o ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/guardiola-thua-liverpool-03-nao-phai-tham-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin