ckground-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh b\u1edfi c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a N\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadt h\u1eb9p.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, Man City \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Pep Guardiola v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 duy tr\u00ec ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng The Citizens v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1, Liverpool gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gieo s\u1ea7u cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Guardiola b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 3-0 b\u1edfi c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah, Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain v\u00e0 Sadio Mane. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n T\u00e2y Ban Nha tin r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Liverpool 5-0 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i sinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Guardiola phat bieu sau tran Liverpool 3-0 Man City hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/HLV-Pep-Guardiola.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Trong c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ai ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng \u0111ang n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n tin r\u1eb1ng Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</em>\u201d, HLV Guardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. \u201c<em>C\u00f2n h\u01a1n 90 ph\u00fat n\u1eefa v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>T\u00f4i d\u00e0nh ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. H\u00f4m nay, b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid, Bayern Munich, Barcelona v\u00e0 Liverpool s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Juventus, Sevilla, Roma v\u00e0 Man City th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00ec \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o n\u00f3.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 3-0 Man City\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Liverpool-3-0-Man-City-Huy-diet-vua-nuoc-Anh,-The-Klopp-tien-gan-vong-ban-ket-hinh-anh-goc-2.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Liverpool 3-0 Man City</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-30-man-city-con-benh-giao-dieu-cua-pep-guardiola-184-183544.html\">Liverpool 3-0 Man City: C\u01a1n b\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tung-bung-vui-dap-man-city-klopp-van-tuc-gian-184-183542.html\">T\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Man City, Klopp v\u1eabn... t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-liverpool-30-man-city-184-183541.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Liverpool 3-0 Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-liverpool-vs-man-city-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183536.html\">K\u1ebf