}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca 4-1 Roma t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- H\u1ea1 Roma 4-1, Barcelona c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 10 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Champions League, ghi 17 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Barca c\u0169ng n\u00e2ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Champions League l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 26 (th\u1eafng 24, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung thong ke an tuong sau tran Barca 4-1 Roma hinh anh\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn Barca 4-1 Roma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Pique-ghi-ban-cho-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pique b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca 4-1 Roma</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n- Kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i, Roma ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 trong s\u1ed1 14 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u (2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qarabag v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i), c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thua 8 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 5 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, cao nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Roma ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 4 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ecbu 2 b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1eeb sau Galatasaray th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 2015 (vs Astana).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn Barca 4-1 Roma \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u Andres Iniesta c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft th\u1ee9 21 t\u1ea1i Champions League, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Ryan Giggs and Xavi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Luis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Champions League sau 10 tr\u1eadn, t\u1ed5ng th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng 1.058 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea3 11 b\u00e0n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Suarez t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Camp Nou c\u1ee7a Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Gerard Pique (12) v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 trong danh s\u00e1ch h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ghi b\u00e0n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t Champions League, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m Roberto Carlos (16) v\u00e0 Ivan Helguera (15).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Barca 4-1 Roma\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca 4-1 Roma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Thong-so-Barca-4-1-Roma.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Barca 4-1 Roma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ket-qua-barcelona-vs-roma-tran-dau-tu-ket-champions-league-201718-184-183535.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Barcelona vs Roma tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-barca-vs-roma-01h45-ngay-54-champions-league-201718-372-183530.html\">Barca 4-1 Roma (KT): Nh\u1eadn l\u1ed9c t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, Blaugrana coi nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-nham-hau-ve-sevilla-thay-umtiti-180-183510.html\">Barca nh\u1eafm h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Sevilla thay Umtiti</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/umtiti-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-griezmann-180-183457.html\">Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Griezmann?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-lo-so-rakitic-se-roi-barca-o-he-2018-180-183428.html\">Messi lo s\u1ee3 Rakitic s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"795","checkdouble":"183550"}]}